      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why im botherin anymore. it's just the same thing every single time. i try to fix things, i try to get a new job or just be better, but i always end up right back here. just stuck in this loop of failing and feeling like shit. feels like im just running in circles for no reason.",
