      "content": "If you are having thoughts of ending your life, please know that there are people who want to support you right now. You can connect with the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline by calling or texting 988 anytime in the US and Canada. In the UK, you can call 111. These services are free, confidential, and available 24/7 to help you through this overwhelming moment. Please reach out to them immediately.",
